text: Chase Foster Ealey (born July 20, 1994) is an American track and field athlete specializing in throwing events. ==Professional== Ealey is the 2019 US outdoor and indoor shot put champion. She is the 2018 United States Indoor 4th-place finisher in the shot put.2018 USA Indoor Track and Field Results USATF Retrieved March 2, 2018Chase Foster Ealey Los Alamos High School Los Alamos, NM
